{"tid":1720741,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇外國撚買左機票番香港投票？","createTime":"2019-11-14T12:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T19:26:52.000Z","uid":42884,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5cf3a1ba0fd8bfe42fec6110d2f72fe5bb0635b0","tid":1720741,"uid":42884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:45:46.000Z","msg":"雖然只係區選，仲要唔知到最後有冇得投。<br />\n但身在外國見香港咁多個月咁樣都做唔到啲野，決定買機票番香港投票。<br />\n如果外國巴有錢有時間，不妨考慮下十一月廿四日番一番香港投個票。"},{"pid":"ec91a92f1cdaaaf0a14dd4ae0503dd673bb4ccf9","tid":1720741,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:46:14.000Z","msg":"［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35748b796e138e8c2edb16eb5a8d4a6ae6a73ac9","tid":1720741,"uid":49979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:48:17.000Z","msg":"我係你我都會咁做"},{"pid":"8fcf80877268efc6c767899f30625928e7da0122","tid":1720741,"uid":42884,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:00:10.000Z","msg":"不論大家喺外國讀書定做野，有錢有時間番一番香港投票呀！"},{"pid":"085c64f6d024ef87d2a6ee7a3f49d0f14757b0b1","tid":1720741,"uid":153781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ebb39ef9a8be1d45fa61152cff3c6562e137e1","tid":1720741,"uid":261478,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:16:13.000Z","msg":"已買<br />\n但怕返到黎無得投<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c36383b4dc6a890dff65501b0b1749bc0c873b","tid":1720741,"uid":42884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70ebb39ef9a8be1d45fa61152cff3c6562e137e1","tid":1720741,"uid":261478,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:16:13.000Z","msg":"已買<br />\n但怕返到黎無得投<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:16:12.000Z","msg":"我都驚，不過唔理照番"},{"pid":"38270a1cd5eaf7855e10cd500edf8215334afcaa","tid":1720741,"uid":159649,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:39:36.000Z","msg":"父母唔比我翻<br />\n但其實我已經買左機票<br />\n諗住再說服下佢哋"},{"pid":"18ddce98326659f503e44194e9e7530de5c8fcdb","tid":1720741,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:39:57.000Z","msg":"[正視聽]邊撚個再話大學據點係佔中2.0或者鼓吹棄守一律為風向分化撚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1721752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1721752</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fd5de1d51d15fd00520f3186828507d17cec2936","tid":1720741,"uid":88420,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:59:42.000Z","msg":"係歐洲 exchange 緊，出發前已經買左機票！<br />\n<br />\n以 21 號起飛，22號返到香港，25號返歐洲計算，好多機票仲係好平。啱啱 search 過票價，住係下面地方嘅手足考慮一下！<br />\n<br />\n- 巴塞隆那（$3500，Air France / KLM）<br />\n- 羅馬（$3500，Air France / KLM)<br />\n- 奧斯陸（$3600，Turkish）<br />\n- 斯德哥爾摩（$3700，Air France / KLM）<br />\n- 巴黎（$3700，British Airways）<br />\n- 阿姆斯特丹（$3800，Air France）<br />\n- 柏林（$3900，British Airways）<br />\n- 倫敦（$3900，Swiss）<br />\n- 法蘭克福（$4000，British Airways）<br />\n- 里斯本（$4200，British Airways）<br />\n- 布魯塞爾（$4300，Air France / KLM)<br />\n- 愛丁堡（$4300，British Airways）<br />\n<br />\n歐洲三間航空公司龍頭，近年係香港航線鬥到痴線。依家少左人黎香港，票價更加低。<br />\n<br />\n住係歐洲嘅手足，無論如何，一齊返香港。好似 2014 年台灣九合一選舉咁，逼爆台北車站返鄉投票咁，好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e639068862c468637f88603fb5e64366931793","tid":1720741,"uid":2110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"38270a1cd5eaf7855e10cd500edf8215334afcaa","tid":1720741,"uid":159649,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:39:36.000Z","msg":"父母唔比我翻<br />\n但其實我已經買左機票<br />\n諗住再說服下佢哋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:00:20.000Z","msg":"唔同佢地講囉，投完票咪去香港周圍行下先返外國，依家無哂班中國旅客真係好舒服架"},{"pid":"624ac6a47ae27e54f22996cdb02ce9629628e71f","tid":1720741,"uid":82706,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:03:11.000Z","msg":"買咗喇，萬幾蚊，返唔夠 24 小時又飛返去<br />\n加拿大東部，拎唔到假，同埋單程飛過黎都至少廿粒鐘"},{"pid":"6056c82b952219ea2b0eec2ac834b751be9633dc","tid":1720741,"uid":41988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:06:08.000Z","msg":"多倫多飛香港來回機票$6000"},{"pid":"a47b94bf4823b43942a63c0e91616c258e060e54","tid":1720741,"uid":42884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6056c82b952219ea2b0eec2ac834b751be9633dc","tid":1720741,"uid":41988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:06:08.000Z","msg":"多倫多飛香港來回機票$6000"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:08:05.000Z","msg":"我紐約番嚟都係$7000幾，不過仲可以連埋Thanksgiving <br />\n<br />\n美國巴打請三日假就可以連埋thanksgiving"},{"pid":"3a1604edfbda632ed7c5a5218ab008c8d9efd8d9","tid":1720741,"uid":48566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:08:57.000Z","msg":"買左，希望有得投"},{"pid":"d9ee35e715eefac048cae561219da1cd291c7ca1","tid":1720741,"uid":42884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:16:22.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"0479da004b23f90cc01511d469b7bec21f37ca99","tid":1720741,"uid":42143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:37:49.000Z","msg":"想買 但係仲諗緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06b0e613af55edfa029ab94454be3b3389fb49a","tid":1720741,"uid":42884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0479da004b23f90cc01511d469b7bec21f37ca99","tid":1720741,"uid":42143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:37:49.000Z","msg":"想買 但係仲諗緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:58:00.000Z","msg":"仲有一星期咋，番嚟啦"},{"pid":"d05b5afab1c9699c49b1bc976720529c6ad2b30f","tid":1720741,"u